<HEADLINE>Tamil held</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>10</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>976601320</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
COLOMBO: Sri Lanka police have arrested a Tamil youth with a blueprint
of Colombo's new twin-tower World Trade Centre. It is thought the man or
an accomplice planned to blast the 39-storey building as did Muslim
extremists at the World Trade Centre in New York two years ago, killing
six people and injuring 1000.
